"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"咱们還有党呀"},{"pid":"d9faa5656486466ae894c34639962ee266b38808","tid":477294,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少林鷹爪功 定係大力金鋼指 ?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係行運超人既軟弱無力拳"},{"pid":"09b0cd0308cda7978a04d34afd73ae900c68863a","tid":477294,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她真的要多謝發展商，試想想，如果發生大地震，成層樓全毀，但裡面所有人安而無樣般走出來，還可以絲絲言倒抽一根紅雙囍香煙，問你服未？</blockquote><br />\n支拿風格文句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df705a458f9656fa089066fa90beca4da844b0d","tid":477294,"uid":82125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"市民： 求求你幫忙呀，我買的樓是發泡膠。<br />\n<br />\n黨：別擔心,來, 看看我們習主席在19大發言，國家將來一定比美國強呀，人民富起來，國家強起來。對了 你身上會不會有撈力士呀，金條呀？<br />\n<br />\n市民：有有有，這裡這裡<br />\n<br />\n黨：別擔心別擔心，我們懂怎麼做， 就算樓倒下了也不要緊，你們一家還有黨吧，金錢重要也不及黨的恩情大，對吧！，先回去等消息吧。"},{"pid":"17e3377dccee14281a4e1c96647c79637b9ab09f","tid":477294,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"外牆飾板好似係就咁鋪上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藍色嗰啲就係建築用發泡膠<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.archiexpo.com/images_ae/photo-m/61705-5841425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.archiexpo.com%2Fimages_ae%2Fphoto-m%2F61705-5841425.jpg&h=4878b5fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0832cfbf6d59ea0de30df8f8df18c9097f64a690","tid":477294,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f62f9d683dd2f05f151df34481c79a639567fba","tid":477294,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外牆飾板好似係就咁鋪上去<img src=\"/asset