/></blockquote><br />\n好似係PVC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢張清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/131814_07466f5c1acf3329265933bae83b64f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F131814_07466f5c1acf3329265933bae83b64f8.jpg&h=12efbd4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39aedb220bcf11f341a267ca541747f32c012199","tid":477294,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>質問「誰家的外牆是軟的？你們想賺多少錢？有沒有良心？」<br />\n<br />\n同中國人講良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每當支那人蝕底,比人搵老襯個陣<br />\n個啲西方價值觀就搬哂出黎<br />\n又良心 又民主 又自由 又人權 又公義<br />\n到佢地要侵略人 拎著數 <br />\n西方價值觀就掉埋一邊"},{"pid":"fb4666fe81de088f1b5d630922fdaab88ad990f8","tid":477294,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而發泡膠是為了營造法式建築風格。</span></span></blockquote><br />\n法國人：???"},{"pid":"7ed46486cee5ae6bfcf0a2246f168416a59271bf","tid":477294,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"咁咪好，防止小朋友撞穿頭"},{"pid":"b5654a297d86ed4eb463d22f54a4f6a16d3a76e6","tid":477294,"uid":95634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:08:59.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個覺得條女好似kibi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eb923e2477389384b00a5e8454d2a5015b9d61","tid":477294,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">五礦地產是（港交所：0230）2013年在香港上市，是中國五礦集團公司旗下公司之一。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n正丫！乜狗屎垃圾公司都嚟香港上市。</blockquote><br />\n國際城市，洗錢又方便"},{"pid":"32e12331901790a71031963c0b80daabbf471727","tid":477294,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外牆飾板好似係就咁鋪上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藍色嗰啲就係建築用發泡膠<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.archiexpo.com/images_ae/photo-m/61705-5841425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.archiexpo.com%2Fimages_ae%2Fphoto-m%2F61705-5841425.jpg&h=4878b5fb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢嗰出面仲有木板喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係PVC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢張清楚啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/131814_07466f5c1acf3329265933bae83b64f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F131814_07466f5c1acf3329265933bae83b64f8.jpg&h=12efbd4e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點睇都唔係就咁polymer foam野外露出下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實理論上如果間屋一半用回收塑膠起，性能同埋成本仲有耐用性應該唔差🤔仲好環保添"},{"pid":"5e27619fc3c284287af435b49eae2887d0e92812","tid":477294,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"印象中外國啲屋喺用木起個框架，用foam 填滿個框架，之後用鋼材加固，出面再上一浸隔熱版(都係polymer foam)然後上內外牆(外面係木/塑膠條，內面係薄水泥板+ polyestyrene film再上油漆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"4fb318754855c549b51f3f3024cd05391aec69d4","tid":477294,"uid":37860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"印象中水泥貴過發泡膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}